    "demo.welcome.card.title": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "✨ Smart RAG Prompt Guide"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "✨ 智能 RAG 提问向导"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "demo.welcome.content": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "# Welcome to ZhiYu 👋\n\nDiscover the magic of true **AI-Native Knowledge Management**. Here, every note you take \"thinks\".\n\n## 🌟 What is ZhiYu?\n\nZhiYu is more than just a beautiful Markdown editor; it is a personal digital brain powered by a built-in **RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)** engine. This means:\n- **Never Forgets**: Drop long documents, articles, or inspirations into ZhiYu, and the system automatically converts them into high-dimensional semantic vectors.\n- **Talk to Your Knowledge**: No more digging through endless folders. Click the AI chat panel and ask, \"Summarize the core of this document,\" or \"Extract last week's research report.\" AI will instantly retrieve and summarize with citations.\n\n## 🚀 Your Magical First Step\n\n1. **Write Freely**: Edit this document or create a new page in the sidebar to experience the buttery smooth writing flow.\n2. **Connect Islands**: Use the `[[Page Name]]` syntax to easily create bi-directional links and watch your knowledge graph grow in real-time.\n3. **Touch of Magic**: Notice the **Guided AI floating button** at the bottom of the page, and initiate your first knowledge chat right now!\n\n---\n> \"We don't just produce knowledge, we synthesize thoughts.\" \n> — ZhiYu Development Team"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "# 欢迎来到智宇 (ZhiYu) 👋\n\n探索真正的**AI 原生知识管理**魔法。在这里，您的每一篇笔记都会“思考”。\n\n## 🌟 什么是智宇？\n\n智宇不仅仅是一个精美的 Markdown 编辑器，它是一个内置了 **RAG (检索增强生成)** 引擎的私人数字大脑。这意味着：\n- **永远不会遗忘**：把长篇文献、文章或灵感抛给智宇，系统会自动将它们转化为高维语义向量，永久铭记。\n- **与知识对话**：您再也无需苦苦翻阅海量文件夹。点击界面上的 AI 对话面板，直接询问“总结这篇文档的核心”、“帮我提炼上周的研究报告”，AI 将像您的助理一样，从海量知识中瞬时提取并带引用总结。\n\n## 🚀 您的魔法第一步\n\n1. **随心记录**：修改这篇文档，或者在侧边栏新建一个页面，体验丝滑的写作感。\n2. **连接孤岛**：使用 `[[页面名称]]` 语法可以轻松创建双向链接，观察左侧图谱的实时生长。\n3. **点石成金**：留意页面底部的 **引导式 AI 浮窗**，立刻对这篇文档发起第一次知识对话提问！\n\n---\n> “我们不生产知识，我们只做思想的合成器。” \n> —— 智宇研发团队"
          }
        }
      }
    },
